=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你依家仲有冇？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"我知你唔係驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認為最重要係&quot;克服&quot;驚果樣野 (即係對我黎講既&quot;死&quot;; 同對你黎講既&quot;驚既感覺&quot;)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"我果時既&quot;克服&quot;未去到睇通睇透,點諗都無事既LEVEL<br />\n咁我咪諗方法等我少D諗<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 我果時沖涼/臨訓果時都會特別多野諗<br />\n咁我咪帶埋部電話入廁所一邊睇youtube一邊沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住等到自己好撚累先上床訓教,一撻上去即訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係無啦啦又瀨野 我會深呼吸先 之後諗其他自己驚既野轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我依家好少了, 雖然專登諗果時都會驚<br />\n但係可以好快轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1f9908d6e86c23eb7003a41f21b0998f4a87f2","tid":2251922,"uid":341236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:17:55.000Z","msg":"從此唔玩過山車跳樓機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主我好似明你？"},{"pid":"9fccd8afec5ca44c40be4c1a47523e28dbc93575","tid":2251922,"uid":71849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"望落似panic attack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8108afaec668666ce2179c8ab86bb1d7990aceed","tid":2251922,"uid":298578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"panic attack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4b47a6fb17cf8b81e3678b10cc9b28a04543cf","tid":2251922,"uid":298578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8108afaec668666ce2179c8ab86bb1d7990aceed","tid":2251922,"uid